<h2>Thank you for submitting an application to become part of our community!</h2>

<h4>Someone will contact you within 2-3 business days after reviewing your submission.</h4>
<h4>Below is an example of how your business will appear upon approval:</h4>

{{#each businessAppPreview.businessess as |business|}}
  <h2 class="biz-name">
    {{business.name}} <br>
  </h2>

  <div class="biz-site">
    <a href={{business.website}}>{{business.website}}</a><br>
  </div>


  <img class="biz-img" src={{business.image}}> <br>

  <div class="biz-description">
    {{business.description}} <br>
  </div>

  <div class="biz-info">
    Hours: {{business.hours}} <br>
    Address: {{business.addr1}} {{business.addr2}} {{business.city}}, {{business.state}} {{business.zip}}<br>


    Phone: {{business.phone}} <br>
    Years in business: {{business.yearsInBusiness}} <br>
  </div>
{{/each}}
